{"tid":2462904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方拘捕香港自由之書女成員　涉洗黑錢達數百萬元","createTime":"2021-03-26T09:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:52:03.000Z","uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b95fad207e0d02b834abd4e00226a126019586d9","tid":2462904,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"警方毒品調查科財富調查組，今日（26日）在元朗橫台山拘捕1名25歲女子，涉嫌洗黑錢數以百萬元。警方稍後將舉行記者會，交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，該名女子為香港自由之書成員，有人在網上發布假消息，包括警方在新屋嶺不合理對待示威者，然後在網上發起眾籌，但實質是用來購買名牌物品。另警方正通緝2名男子，該2人已逃往美國。<br />\n<br />\n東網唔貼"},{"pid":"91fca27365bc25e7a50b4c29a3e81b55d08b9691","tid":2462904,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81995f9cb9422441dcf0bd0a381ee2cd5c4a9316","tid":2462904,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b6c41f274a7ac3430ffeb202fb440baf772d25","tid":2462904,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"我信佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"